### ============================================================================
### Step 6: Check Client's information
### ============================================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/client/info
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}

### ============================================================================
### Step 7: Admin Regenerates API Key
### Tests key rotation.
### ============================================================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/clients/{{client_id}}/key
Authorization: Bearer {{masterKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================================================
### Step 8: Admin Deletes Client
### Tests data isolation and cascading cleanup.
### ============================================================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/clients/{{client_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{masterKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

